<CO>
   AVP EUROP
</CO>
<IN>
HOUSEHOLD AND PERSONAL-CARE PRODUCTS (HHP)
</IN>
<LP>
   NEW YORK -- Avon Products Inc. said it is introducing its
cosmetics and door-to-door selling operation in East Germany,
as it continues to bring Avon to Eastern Europe. Earlier this
month, Avon began to sell its cosmetics in Hungary.
</LP>
