<HL>
   Who's News:
   Houghton Mifflin Co.
</HL>
<DATE>
04/26/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
<CO>
   HTN WNEWS
</CO>
<LP>
   HOUGHTON MIFFLIN Co. (Boston) -- This publishing company
named DeRoy C. Thomas, president and chief operating officer
of ITT Corp., as a director. He succeeds David S. Saxon, who
retired.
</LP>
