indicating only that Tompson Pacific, a property investment
and investment holding company, is in talks to buy 34.5% of
BCIL. The report also said Bond Corp. is in discussions to
place the remaining 31.5% with unrelated parties.
   Trading in shares of BCIL and Tompson Pacific was stopped
before the start of yesterday's session and will remain
halted until further details are disclosed, the companies
said.
